tourists from the Commonwealth of Independent States, experts said.
</P>
<P>
Besides, an increased number of foreign visitors will rush to
southern Turkey for brilliant sunshine and golden beaches in the
summer holiday season.
</P>
<P>
To help secure a tourist boom, experts have called for
coordination of local governments, travel agencies and hotels,
and active image advertisement campaigns abroad. 
