180 million shares from Friday's 340 million shares, as foreign
investors stayed on the sidelines due to Easter holidays.
</P>
<P>
The Nikkei Stock Average of 225 selected issues on the First
Section of the Tokyo Stock Exchange fell 163.54 points, or 0.99
percent from last Friday's close to 16,317.58.
</P>
<P>
