<HEADLINE> Dhaka Studies Measures to Boost Frozen Food Export </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, April 13 (Xinhua) -- The Bangladeshi government is
examining a package of measures to boost the country's export of
frozen food, one of the country's major foreign exchange earners,
the Commerce Ministry said Monday.
</P>
<P>
