<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 13 (Xinhua) -- The Beijing Marine Aquarium, the
largest of its kind in China, is expected to be completed and open
to visitors in the last quarter of this year.
</P>
<P>
The aquarium, a joint venture between Beijing Zoo and a Hong
kong company, covers 35,000 square meters in area and has a floor
space of 42,000 square meters.
</P>
