more than 80,000 square meters. Construction of the project
started in 1994.
</P>
<P>
The aquarium has a marine theater, with 3,000 seats, where the
visitors can view performances by dolphins, sea lions and whales.
</P>
<P>
More than 50,000 fish including 800 species of sea fish and 500
fresh water fish will be exhibited at the aquarium.  
