<HEADLINE> Beijing to Host Monetary Technologies, Equipment Expo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 13 (Xinhua) -- An international exhibition of
monetary technologies and equipment is to be staged from August 30
to September 2 in Beijing's China International Exhibition Center.
</P>
<P>
Sources from the People's Bank of China (PBOC), the sponsor,
said that the exhibition aims to accelerate the process of China's
modernization of financial tools.
</P>
